ConstValues.value: "The advertising identifier is an alphanumeric string that’s unique to each device, and which is only used for advertising.  This string is used for frequency capping, attribution, conversion events, estimating the number of unique users, advertising fraud detection, and debugging.  Devices must request tracking authorization before it can get this identifier."
